            <div class="container">
                <!--<h3  class="center-text"><u style="align:center!important;">ADDENDUM</u></h3>-->
                <p align="center">
                    <STRONG><u>ADDENDUM</u></STRONG>
                </p>
                <p>This addendum agreement
                    <STRONG>("Addendum")</STRONG> is made at New Delhi on<strong>&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,MM'/'dd'/'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!TODAY()}" /></apex:outputText></strong> ("Effective Date") by and between:</p>
                <p><strong>{!accObj.Legal_Name__c}</strong> a ({!accObj.Business_Entity__r.Name}) having its registered office at &nbsp;
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.Address_Line__c!=null && regParentAddress.Address_Line__c!='', regParentAddress.Address_Line__c + ', ', null)}"/>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.City__c!=null && regParentAddress.City__c!='', regParentAddress.City__c + ', ', null)}"/>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.State__c!=null && regParentAddress.State__c!='', regParentAddress.State__c + ', ', null)}"/>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.Country__c!=null && regParentAddress.Country__c!='', regParentAddress.Country__c, null)}"/>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.Country__c!=null && regParentAddress.Pincode__c!=null, ' - ', null)}"/>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(regParentAddress.Pincode__c!=null && regParentAddress.Pincode__c!='', regParentAddress.Pincode__c, null)}"/>
                    (hereinafter referred to as <strong>"Merchant"</strong>, which expression shall, unless repugnant to the context thereof, include its successors-in-interest and permitted assigns);</p>
                <p><strong>AND</strong></p>
                <p><strong>PayU Payments Private Limited,</strong> a company incorporated under the Companies Act, 1956 having its registered office at 2nd Floor, P&amp;G Plaza Cardinal Gracious Road, Chakala, Andheri (East) Mumbai, Mumbai City, Maharashtra, Pin-400099 and corporate office at 9th Floor, Bestech Business Tower, Sector 48, Sohna Road, Gurgaon, Haryana, Pin - 122002 (hereinafter referred to as <strong>"PayU"</strong>, which expression shall, unless repugnant to the context thereof, include its successors-in-interest and assigns);</p>
                <p>(PayU and the Merchant are hereinafter collectively referred to as <strong>"Parties"</strong> and individually as <strong>"Party"</strong>.) </p>
                <p><strong>WHEREAS:</strong></p>
                <table cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">A.</td>
                        <td>The Parties had entered into a referral agreement dated<strong>&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="{0,date,MM'/'dd'/'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!TODAY()}" /></apex:outputText></strong> executed between the Parties (hereinafter referred to as "Referral Agreement”) wherein PayU is providing aggregate payment gateway services to prospective merchants referred by the Merchant on the terms as defined under the Referral Agreement.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">B.</td>
                        <td>The Parties are now desirous of amending the provisions of the Referral Agreement as per the below mentioned term and conditions.</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>NOW THEREFORE, IN CONSIDERATION OF THE MUTUAL COVENANTS, TERMS AND CONDITIONS AND UNDERSTANDINGS SET FORTH IN THIS ADDENDUM AND OTHER GOOD AND VALUABLE CONSIDERATION (THE RECEIPT AND ADEQUACY OF WHICH ARE HEREBY MUTUALLY ACKNOWLEDGED), THE PARTIES WITH THE INTENT TO BE LEGALLY BOUND HEREBY AGREE AS FOLLOWS:</strong></p>
                <table cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
                    <tr>
                        <td valign = "top">1.</td>
                        <td>The Parties, from the Effective Date of this Addendum, mutually agrees for addition of Sub- Clause of Clause 5 in the Referral Agreement, which shall be read as follows:-<br/><br/>
                        "The Referrer acknowledges, undertakes and confirms that the credentials/ information/ or any other data of Prospective Merchant (“Prospective Merchant Information”) shall be shared by PayU with the Referrer under the terms of this Agreement. The Referrer shall be solely responsible to protect and maintain the integrity of the Prospective Merchant Information. Any loss incurred to PayU due to any breach by the Referrer (including its employees, contractors, agents etc.) of the obligations set out under this clause shall be borne solely by the Referrer and the Referrer agrees to indemnify, defend and hold harmless PayU from any claims, actions, damages or losses arising out or in relation thereto. Such obligation upon Referrer shall survive after the termination or expiry of this Agreement"
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">2.</td>
                        <td>The provisions of this Addendum shall become effective from the Effective Date.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">3.</td>
                        <td>This Addendum shall be read in conjunction with the Agreement and be enforced as if the provisions of this Addendum were incorporated therein by way of an amendment/ addition.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">4.</td>
                        <td>Capitalized words and expressions used and not defined in this Addendum but defined in the Referral Agreement shall have the same meaning as respectively assigned to them in the Referral Agreement.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">5.</td>
                        <td>The Referral Agreement is amended only to the extent specifically set forth herein. All other terms and conditions in the Agreement shall remain in full force and effect and shall not be superseded by this Addendum in the event of a conflict between the terms and conditions of this Addendum and those contained in the Referral Agreement, the terms and conditions of this Addendum shall prevail.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">6.</td>
                        <td>This Addendum shall be governed by the same provisions on notices, confidentiality, governing law, jurisdiction and arbitration as provisioned under the Referral Agreement.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">7.</td>
                        <td>This Addendum is co-terminus with the Referral Agreement. In the event the Referral Agreement is terminated, this Addendum shall terminate on its own.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td valign="top">8.</td>
                        <td>This Addendum may be executed in two counterparts, each of which taken together shall constitute a single instrument.</td>
                    </tr>
                    
                </table>
                <p><strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF</strong> the Parties hereto have executed this Addendum through their Authorized Signatories on the day, month and year first herein mentioned above: </p><br/>
